<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٩٦ - مَنْ جَالَسَ عَالِمًا فَكَأَنَّمَا جَالَسَ نَبِيًّا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>لَا يُعْرَفُ لَكِنْ جَاءَ عَنِ الشَّافِعِيِّ - رَضِيَ اللَّهُ عَنْهُ - إِذَا رَأَيْتَ رَجُلا مِنْ أَصْحَابِ الْحَدِيثِ فَكَأَنَّمَا رَأَيْت النَّبِي - صلى الله عَلَيْهِ وَسلم - "<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٤٩٧ - مَنْ جَدَّ وَجَدَ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَرُبَّمَا قِيلَ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٤٩٨ - مَنْ طَلَبَ وَجَدَّ وَجَدَ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>هُوَ بِمَعْنَى<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٤٩٩ - لِكُلِّ مُجْتَهِدٍ نَصِيبٌ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَلَيْسَا فِي الْحَدِيثِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٥٠٠ - مَنْ جَمَعَ مَالا مِنْ نَهَاوِشَ - أَيْ بِكَسْرِ الْوَاوِ - أَذْهَبَهُ اللَّهُ فِي نَهَابِرَ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>قَالَ السُّبْكِيُّ لَا أَصْلَ لَهُ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>